-- German Government Reviewing Legal Rules for Publishing Bank Stress Tests
-- Tony Czuczka
-- 2010-06-18T09:48:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/german-government-reviewing-legal-rules-for-publishing-bank-stress-tests.html

          
          
             Germany is reviewing the legal rules
for publishing bank stress tests, the Finance Ministry said.  
 “We will look at what has to be changed” in German law,
Ministry spokesman Michael Offer told reporters in Berlin today.
He said that as far as he understands, critics of stress tests
are changing their minds.  
